<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.5.5">
<l>pakkanōkki niṟku naiyumeṉ ṟaṉṉaiya rumuṉitir</l>
<l>takkakīrttit tirukku ṟuṅkuṭi nampiyai nāṉkaṇṭapiṉ</l>
<l>ṟokkacōtit toṇṭai vāyu nīṇṭa puruvaṅkaḷun</l>
<l>takkatāmaraik kaṇṇum pāviyē ṉāviyiṉ mēlaṉavē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“She stands looking at the side, languishes”, so you all disapprove, mothers.</l>
<l>After I saw Nampi of Tirukkuṟuṅkuṭi with befitting fame,</l>
<l>the caper[-pink] mouth with accumulated light, the elongated brows</l>
<l>and the befitting lotus eyes are on the soul of me evildoer.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
